Royal Resources Corp said itexercised an option to buy all of the common stock of MontaguMining Investments Inc, whose primary asset is a ten pctinterest in Hog Ranch gold mine in Washoe County, Nevada.    Royal said it paid 3.6 mln dlrs in cash plus 200,000 sharesof Royal Resources common stock for the interest.    Montagu Mining is a subsidiary of London-based SamuelMontagu Ltd.    Hog Ranch is a joint venture gold mine which has been inoperation since March 1986 and is currently producing gold at arate of more than 50,000 ounces a year, it said. Reuter&#3;